    "last_edited_by": {
      "object": "user",
      "id": "a89840a5-a507-41f8-ad65-4d62341efbc9"
    },
    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "A few times I find myself so far down the beach after a wave and the only option is a walk around. When you pass the end of the rocks it’s always possible to kick out and then have a shorter paddle against the rip back up to the takeoff point - but when I’m on the wave this is never an option that goes through my mind. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "A few times I find myself so far down the beach after a wave and the only option is a walk around. When you pass the end of the rocks it’s always possible to kick out and then have a shorter paddle against the rip back up to the takeoff point - but when I’m on the wave this is never an option that goes through my mind. ",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
